      <p>
The 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_physical_activity_vital_sign">Physical Activity Vital Sign</xref>
 is an 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_assessment_tool">ASSESSMENT TOOL</xref>.        </p>
      <p>
The 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_physical_activity_vital_sign">Physical Activity Vital Sign</xref>
 (<xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_physical_activity_vital_sign">PAVS</xref>) is a tool designed to screen for physical activity in adult 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENTS</xref>.        </p>
      <p>
For further information on the 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_physical_activity_vital_sign">Physical Activity Vital Sign</xref>, see 
              <xref href="http://www.exerciseismedicine.org/assets/page_documents/The%20Physical%20Activity%20Vital%20Sign%20without%20Strength_2015_07_09_PDF.pdf"
               scope="external"
               format="html">Physical Activity Vital Sign</xref>.        </p>
